Title: Worldsoul: Nerub-ar Palace
Description:
Queen Ansurek has proven herself both cruel and cunning. We cannot allow her forces to continue to grow in strength with Xal'atath's black blood. 

It has come to this. A daunting task indeed. With the greatest of our forces, we shall lay siege to Nerub-ar Palace!
ObjectivesText: Complete the Nerub-ar Palace raid on Heroic difficulty or higher.
